{"tid":271734,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[阿仙奴]23歲渡邊麻友開始劣化 性感谷劇被嫌似30路","createTime":"2017-06-05T10:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T13:49:40.000Z","uid":333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf807284e9b0e26ac306f473f8ec66c6886d9bb0","tid":271734,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"日本組合AKB48一年一度嘅「第9屆AKB人氣總選」已定本月17日舉行，日前公佈速報成績所見，NGT48嘅18歲成員荻野由佳暫時爆大冷以5.5萬票拋離其他成員，松井珠理奈、指原莉乃緊隨其後，渡邊麻友只得2萬7千票排第四位。<br />\n<br />\n渡邊麻友呢排明顯冇運行，由佢主演嘅深夜劇《永別了江成》收視欠佳，開播前已因前劇名而引起秋田縣不滿而要臨時改名，最新播出嘅第六集得2%，上集更只得1.7%低收視，下集麻友將有性感演出，未知能否挽救收視。不過，只得23歲嘅麻友近排被指劣化，演出新劇時更似個中女，與兩三年前全盛時期嘅可愛樣貌有頗大出入，網民認為現時嘅佢橫睇掂睇都起碼30幾歲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/180653_fd4bf9e70fb8e6f776592e1040badd9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F180653_fd4bf9e70fb8e6f776592e1040badd9e.jpg&h=d78aad7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea60b6eb890bf9146cbedd71177c51867c94c80b","tid":271734,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"g<br />\nold g"},{"pid":"64a12cdc19f60cd67f63529505770e4559555534","tid":271734,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>g<br />\nold g</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d69432d36f430af469a279f02b4516a99c540ad","tid":271734,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7fc0ea0de05c9b0ce814cc9ce5f53899e2f61fe","tid":271734,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29651f3ec2cf7ecacf473da109a9263e5320c460","tid":271734,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:37:05.000Z","ms